Wait, wait, wait, wait.

01:09:53.737 --> 01:09:55.855
- Ready? All right. Lets do this.
- Wait, wait. Ready.

01:09:55.935 --> 01:09:57.333
- Come on. Come on.
- Ready.

01:09:57.453 --> 01:09:58.931
Give it to me!

01:09:59.051 --> 01:10:00.809
No! Wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait!

01:10:00.889 --> 01:10:02.686
- Remember what we talked about?
To the side.
- I know.

01:10:02.806 --> 01:10:04.604
- How many times
we gonna go over this?
- Okay.

01:10:04.724 --> 01:10:06.602
Stop. Just--
All right. Trust me, okay?

01:10:06.682 --> 01:10:09.239
- All right. I'm ready.
- Trust me. I got this shit. Ready?

01:10:09.359 --> 01:10:12.155
- Wait, wait, wait!
- I'm about to cut your throat, boy!

01:10:12.275 --> 01:10:14.273
Stop acting like a little girl.
Come on. Come on!

01:10:14.353 --> 01:10:16.990
- You're right, you're right,
you’re right. Yeah, come on!
- Come on. You ready?

01:10:17.069 --> 01:10:20.546
No! You guys are psychos!

01:10:20.626 --> 01:10:22.743
You've seen
one too many TV shows!

01:10:22.863 --> 01:10:26.938
No! Watching television shows
doesn't create psycho killers!

01:10:27.058 --> 01:10:29.296
Cancelin' TV shows does!

01:10:29.415 --> 01:10:31.613
The Wayans Brothers
was a good show, man!

01:10:31.692 --> 01:10:36.048
It was a good-ass show,
and we didn't even get a final episode!

01:10:36.168 --> 01:10:39.205
Take it easy!
I'm feelin' a little woozy here!

01:10:39.284 --> 01:10:41.961
Its my turn.
Give me the knife.

01:10:42.081 --> 01:10:44.918
Fuck outta here.
Ain't nobody stabbin' me.

01:10:50.671 --> 01:10:53.108
- [Cindy Screams] 
- [Ray, Bobby Groaning] 

01:10:53.227 --> 01:10:55.664
Surprise, Cindy!

