All right, all right.
Hold on a second.

01:11:49.402 --> 01:11:51.839
Just give me a moment.
Ah. One--

01:11:53.997 --> 01:11:57.153
[Grunting, Sighing] 

01:11:57.273 --> 01:11:59.391
[Bones Cracking] 
Oh, yeah. That's it.

01:11:59.510 --> 01:12:02.388
Ah. Okay.

01:12:02.467 --> 01:12:05.103
[Cindy Shouting] 

01:12:07.741 --> 01:12:11.296
[Irish Jig Plays] 

01:12:22.204 --> 01:12:25.439
[Shouting] 

01:12:34.390 --> 01:12:36.507
- [Screams] 
- Dad!

01:12:36.587 --> 01:12:38.944
- [Mumbling, Gasping] 
- Are you okay?

01:12:39.064 --> 01:12:41.821
I thought I told you
not to have a party unless I was here.

01:12:41.941 --> 01:12:44.298
But, Dad, you were here.
You were in the closet.

01:12:44.377 --> 01:12:47.734
Oh, yeah, that's right. Did you get some
girlfriends numbers for me?

01:12:47.853 --> 01:12:50.771
- Dad, they're dead.
- Ah, you know, I cant get a break.

