Help me up now.

01:12:55.805 --> 01:12:58.801
Uh-- Uh-- If the cops come, tell em
I'm a plumber, okay?

01:12:58.921 --> 01:13:02.517
You had a leaky faucet, and you
called, and they sent me over.
