01:13:02.637 --> 01:13:05.153
[Sirens Continue] 

01:13:08.110 --> 01:13:11.466
- No! No!
- [Tires Screeching] 

01:13:11.547 --> 01:13:13.464
Dad, Dad, put your arms down.

01:13:15.821 --> 01:13:18.897
- What the hells goin' on here?
-[Man] Sheriff, it’s a bloodbath in there.

01:13:19.017 --> 01:13:20.855
- He was right here! I swear it!
- Who was?

01:13:20.935 --> 01:13:24.171
