The guy that murdered all my friends!

01:13:24.251 --> 01:13:27.807
And the sick bastard planted drugs
all in the house there.

01:13:27.887 --> 01:13:30.684
- All over the place.
- Dad. Stop it.

01:13:30.804 --> 01:13:33.440
All right, Cindy.
I'm gonna have to take you
down to the station.

01:13:33.560 --> 01:13:35.478
I'm cool, though, right?

01:13:35.598 --> 01:13:37.475
- I'm okay?
- Lets-- Lets go, Cindy.

01:13:37.556 --> 01:13:39.793
Cindy. Call me.

01:13:41.152 --> 01:13:42.989
Daddy'll get you out, honey.

01:13:45.386 --> 01:13:49.182
Okay. Lets go over this again.

01:14:01.208 --> 01:14:03.046
- You say it was an accident.
- Yes.

01:14:03.125 --> 01:14:06.162
- He was on the road.
- And you think he came back
to get revenge?

01:14:06.282 --> 01:14:08.999
- It has to be him, Sheriff.
- [Banging] 

01:14:14.353 --> 01:14:16.350
Here, Sheriff.
They wanted me to give this to you.

01:14:16.430 --> 01:14:19.347
- That’ll be all, Doofy.
- Okay.

01:14:19.467 --> 01:14:21.784
- I'm gonna go, then. All right.
- All right.

01:14:22.942 --> 01:14:24.741
Bye, Cindy.

01:14:27.816 --> 01:14:30.094
I’m sorry, Cindy.
It wasn't the man you guys killed.

01:14:30.214 --> 01:14:33.491
His name was David Keegan.
Some fishermen found his body
a few weeks later.

01:14:33.611 --> 01:14:36.886
- He's buried in Lakewood Cemetery.
- That's impossible.

01:14:39.164 --> 01:14:41.441
- Then I don't know who it could be.
- He's gotta be someone else...

01:14:41.561 --> 01:14:44.798
who was connected with all the victims,
someone who knew about the accident.

01:14:44.917 --> 01:14:47.434
Someone who could move around
without being noticed.

01:14:49.672 --> 01:14:52.667
Oh, my God.

01:14:52.747 --> 01:14:56.424
She used to baby-sit my brother Doofy.
He had the biggest crush on her.

01:14:56.543 --> 01:14:59.301
[Gasping] Its me, Cindy.

01:14:59.380 --> 01:15:00.898
Night, Cindy.

01:15:04.654 --> 01:15:06.651
- Doofy!
- Shit head?

01:15:09.808 --> 01:15:11.646
- Have you seen Doofy?
- No.

01:15:11.725 --> 01:15:13.843
- Have you seen Doofy?
Has anybody seen Doofy?
- No, Sheriff.

01:15:13.924 --> 01:15:16.320
- No.
- [Man] Yeah.
Just went out the back, Sheriff.

01:15:16.440 --> 01:15:18.558
[Sheriff] Doofy!

01:15:31.102 --> 01:15:34.339
He walks alone
under the big city lights

01:15:34.459 --> 01:15:38.016
